data.name: LATEX SURGICAL GLOVES
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Natural Rubber

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile Gamma (R) Sterilization

## PRESENTATIONS
- Powder and Powder free
- Rouph and Smooth Surface

## PERFORMANCE
- Aseptic, non-sterile
- Soft and Stretch Sensation
- Tear-Resistant
- Strict monitored Protein Content
- Outstanding tactile sensitivity
- Polymer Coated => Easy Wearing
- Anatomic
